author: stsp
msg: (apply_one_patch): Rename TARGET output parameter to PATCH_TARGET.
Add a local variable TARGET. Stop using a pointer to a pointer
all over the place just to save us from assigning the output
variable before we return. Lots of code churn, I know, sorry.
But it looks prettier this way.
